exting is confusing. When you can only read the words somebody types, without \
seeing their face or hearing their voice, it’s so hard to truly understand what 
they’re trying to say. That’s why texts don’t always get across the message the texter intends.
Thankfully, I’m here to explain some common text-message greetings to all you novice texters and/or\
alien life forms who plan to take over the earth some day with texting.
